@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rqcliv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v0 * (0.43 - (v1 + 0.88 / v1 + 0.31)))
    v1 = 0.22
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.14 * v2 + 0.18) + tmp) - wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.14)))
    data[tid] = v0
